sequenceDiagram
    participant Merchant as 👨‍💼 Merchant
    participant Terminal as 🏪 NFC Terminal
    participant Watch as ⌚ Your Watch
    participant You as 👤 You
    
    Note over Merchant,You: PHASE 2: OFFLINE PAYMENT (5 seconds, NO INTERNET)
    
    Merchant->>Terminal: Enters amount: ₹50
    Terminal->>Terminal: Generates TransactionID (UUID)
    Terminal->>Terminal: Creates payment request with Nonce (random value)
    
    Terminal->>Terminal: Activates NFC reader (13.56 MHz)
    Note over Terminal: NFC = Near Field Communication (4-10cm range)
    
    Merchant->>You: "Tap your watch on terminal"
    You->>Watch: Brings watch near terminal
    
    Watch->>Watch: Detects NFC field ✓
    Watch->>Terminal: NFC handshake established
    Terminal->>Watch: Sends: {MerchantID, Amount:50, Nonce, Timestamp}
    
    Watch->>Watch: Receives NFC data
    Watch->>Watch: Validates: Amount ≤ ₹200? ✓ Balance ≥ ₹50? ✓
    Watch->>Watch: Display: "Payment Request - Tea Shop ₹50?"
    Watch->>Watch: Vibration alert + audio tone
    
    You->>Watch: Taps watch to confirm (gesture recognition)
    Watch->>Watch: Triggers Secure Element
    
    Note over Watch: === CRYPTOGRAPHIC SIGNING (Inside Secure Element) ===
    Watch->>Watch: Create Payment Certificate
    Note over Watch: {MerchantID, Amount:50, TransactionID,<br/>Timestamp(local), User_UUID, Nonce}
    
    Watch->>Watch: Hash certificate (SHA-256)
    Watch->>Watch: Sign hash with Private Key (ECDSA-P256)
    Note over Watch: Signature = Math proof this is real and from this watch
    
    Watch->>Watch: Encrypt signature + certificate (AES-256)
    Watch->>Terminal: NFC transmission: encrypted envelope
    Note over Watch,Terminal: Payload: {Certificate, Signature, Checksum}
    
    Terminal->>Terminal: Receive NFC packet
    Terminal->>Terminal: Decrypt envelope
    Terminal->>Terminal: Retrieve User Public Key (cached from RBI)
    Terminal->>Terminal: Verify ECDSA Signature
    Note over Terminal: If math doesn't match → REJECTED
    
    alt Signature Valid
        Terminal->>Terminal: ✓ Signature verified
        Terminal->>Terminal: Validate Timestamp (±30 sec window)
        Terminal->>Terminal: Verify Nonce matches
        Terminal->>Terminal: Verify Amount = ₹50
        Terminal->>Terminal: Display: "✓ PAYMENT AUTHORIZED"
        Terminal->>Merchant: Green screen + receipt
    else Signature Invalid
        Terminal->>Terminal: ❌ SIGNATURE FAILED
        Terminal->>Terminal: Display: "❌ Payment Rejected"
        Terminal->>Watch: No confirmation sent
    end
    
    Terminal->>Terminal: Store transaction locally
    Note over Terminal: {TransactionID, MerchantID:TEA_001,<br/>Amount:50, Timestamp, Signature}
    
    Watch->>Watch: Update LocalLedger
    Note over Watch: {TransactionID, MerchantID, Amount:50,<br/>Status: PENDING_SYNC}
    
    Watch->>Watch: Deduct balance: ₹500 - ₹50 = ₹450
    Watch->>Watch: Display: "✓ ₹50 Paid - Balance: ₹450"
    Watch->>Watch: Success tone + haptic feedback
    
    Merchant->>User: "Thank you! Your tea is ready"
    
    Note over Merchant,You: ✓ COMPLETE (OFFLINE)<br/>Payment verified by cryptographic signature<br/>NO bank connection needed<br/>NO fraud possible (math proves authenticity)
